              d="M21,6.77573131 C20.338616,7.07692308 19.6265188,7.28060672 18.8795563,7.3716143 C19.6423666,6.9035753 20.2276809,6.16143012 20.5034337,5.27735645 C19.7892235,5.71072589 19,6.02600217 18.1568938,6.19501625 C17.4849445,5.45937161 16.5245642,5 15.461701,5 C13.4236661,5 11.770206,6.69555796 11.770206,8.78656555 C11.770206,9.08342362 11.8019017,9.3716143 11.8652932,9.64897075 C8.79609086,9.4907909 6.07554147,7.98483207 4.25303751,5.69122427 C3.93502377,6.2524377 3.75330164,6.9035753 3.75330164,7.59696641 C3.75330164,8.91007584 4.40517697,10.0693391 5.39619651,10.7486457 C4.79186476,10.7302275 4.22134179,10.5579632 3.72266244,10.276273 L3.72266244,10.3228602 C3.72266244,12.1581798 4.9957739,13.6890574 6.68621236,14.035753 C6.37665082,14.1245937 6.05018489,14.1690141 5.71315372,14.1690141 C5.47543582,14.1690141 5.24300053,14.1462622 5.01796091,14.1018418 C5.4881141,15.6056338 6.85103011,16.7009751 8.46751189,16.7302275 C7.20390914,17.7464789 5.61067089,18.3521127 3.88114105,18.3521127 C3.58320127,18.3521127 3.28843106,18.3347779 3,18.3001083 C4.63444268,19.3726977 6.57633386,20 8.66085578,20 C15.4543053,20 19.1679873,14.2307692 19.1679873,9.22643554 C19.1679873,9.06175515 19.1648177,8.89707476 19.1584786,8.73564464 C19.8800845,8.20151679 20.5066033,7.53521127 21,6.77573131"
