    <figcaption class="component--pullquote__attribution">Sam Ames, director of advocacy and government affairs at the Trevor Project</figcaption>
    <blockquote class="component--pullquote__text"><span>When we’re normalizing and de-stigmatizing things like drag shows, we're helping to create supportive environments.</span></blockquote>
    
    <div class="component--pullquote__icon" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 43.9 35.3" role="img">
        <title>Quote icon</title>
        <style>
          .icon--quote {
            fill: var(--theme-color, #009bff);
