						d="M10.913 12.8449L5.85482 9.92459C5.94907 9.63336 6 9.32263 6 9C6 8.67999 5.9499 8.37169 5.8571 8.0825L10.9184 5.16034C11.4579 5.68026 12.1916 6 13 6C14.6569 6 16 4.65685 16 3C16 1.34315 14.6569 0 13 0C11.3431 0 10 1.34315 10 3C10 3.12468 10.0076 3.24759 10.0224 3.36828L4.63044 6.48131C4.16105 6.17683 3.60117 6 3 6C1.34315 6 0 7.34315 0 9C0 10.6569 1.34315 12 3 12C3.59824 12 4.15559 11.8249 4.62357 11.5231L10.0214 14.6396C10.0073 14.7577 10 14.878 10 15C10 16.6569 11.3431 18 13 18C14.6569 18 16 16.6569 16 15C16 13.3431 14.6569 12 13 12C12.1889 12 11.4529 12.3219 10.913 12.8449Z" />
