        </div>
        </a>
        
    </div>
    
    <figcaption class="component--pullquote__attribution">City of Roanoke public statement</figcaption>
    <blockquote class="component--pullquote__text"><span>We recognize and understand the concerns expressed by the community that this activity fails to reflect the family values and caring culture that the city of Roanoke is committed to maintaining.</span></blockquote>
    
